"title": "5326: government",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5326: government",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's gracious rule over the nations, particularly Israel. Also, the divinely established ruling of people by God's appointed authorities for the good of society and to prevent anarchy.</p>\n<h2>God governs the nations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:28\">PSA 22:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:6\">2CH 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7-Ps9:8\">PSA 9:7–9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:2\">PSA 47:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:7-Ps47:8\">PSA 47:7–47:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:7\">PSA 66:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps67:4\">PSA 67:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:19\">PSA 103:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:32\">DAN 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:35\">DAN 4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15\">1TI 6:15</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ also governs the nations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">ISA 9:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:8-Ps72:11\">PSA 72:8–72:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:2\">PSA 110:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:13\">ZEC 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:27\">REV 2:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:9\">PSA 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:5\">REV 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:15\">REV 19:15</a></p>\n<h2>The manner of God's government of Israel was unique</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:23\">JDG 8:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:7\">1SA 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:12\">1SA 12:12</a></p>\n<h2>God governs individuals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:1\">PRO 21:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:1\">PRO 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:9\">PRO 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:21\">PRO 19:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:24\">PRO 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:23\">JER 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:37\">LAM 3:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:15\">JAS 4:13–4:15</a></p>\n<h2>God has established human agencies for the government of people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:5-Gen9:6\">GEN 9:5–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:15-Prov8:16\">PRO 8:15–8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37-Dan2:38\">DAN 2:37–2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:17\">DAN 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:32\">DAN 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:21\">DAN 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:17-Matt22:21\">MAT 22:17–22:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:11\">JHN 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:2-1Tim2:3\">1TI 2:2–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13\">1PE 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Government is for the good of society</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:4\">ROM 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:12-Ps72:14\">PSA 72:12–72:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:3–82:4</a></p>\n<h3>Government is established to prevent anarchy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:2-Rom13:3\">ROM 13:2–13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">GEN 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:26\">EZR 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:15\">PRO 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:2\">PRO 28:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:4\">PRO 29:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:11\">ACT 25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:4\">ROM 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:14</a></p>",
